msgid "Bridge"
msgstr "Passerelle"

msgid "Channel Sets"
msgstr "Ensemble des canaux"

msgid "Data Channels"
msgstr "Canaux de données"

msgid "Define data channels over which outbound filtered packets will flow."
msgstr ""
"Définissez les canaux de données sur lesquels les paquets filtrés sortants "
"seront acheminés."

msgid ""
"Define filter rules to apply to outbound packets. Matching packets will flow "
"over the data channel."
msgstr ""
"Définissez les règles de filtrage à appliquer aux paquets sortants. Les "
"paquets correspondants passeront sur le canal de données."

msgid "Define primary channels and their corresponding data channels."
msgstr ""
"Définissez les canaux principaux et leurs canaux de données correspondants."

msgid "Destination port"
msgstr "Port de destination"

msgid "Dual Channel Wi-Fi AP Daemon"
msgstr "Démon de l'AP Wi-Fi à double canal"

msgid "Dual Channel WiFi"
msgstr "Wifi double canal"

msgid "Enable"
msgstr "Activer"

msgid "Filter Sets"
msgstr "Ensembles de filtres"

msgid "Filters"
msgstr "Filtres"

msgid "General"
msgstr "Général"

msgid "General Settings"
msgstr "Réglages généraux"

msgid "Grant UCI access for luci-app-dcwapd"
msgstr "Donner l'accès UCI à luci-app-dcwapd"

msgid "Interfaces"
msgstr "Interfaces"

msgid "MAC Address"
msgstr "Adresse MAC"

msgid "Packet size"
msgstr "Taille du paquet"

msgid "Protocol"
msgstr "Protocole"

msgid "SSID"
msgstr "SSID"

msgid "Select filters to apply to matching MAC addresses."
msgstr "Sélectionnez les filtres à appliquer aux adresses MAC correspondantes."

msgid "Source IP"
msgstr "Adresse IP source"

msgid "Source port"
msgstr "Port source"

msgid "Specify the temporary directory for dcwapd file storage."
msgstr ""
"Indiquez le répertoire temporaire pour le stockage des fichiers dcwapd."

msgid "Temp Directory"
msgstr "Répertoire temporaire"

msgid ""
"With %s you can use two simultaneous Wi-Fi connections to decrease wireless "
"traffic congestion and increase throughput."
msgstr ""

#~ msgid ""
#~ "With <abbr title=\"Dual Channel Wi-Fi AP Daemon\">Dual Channel WiFi</"
#~ "abbr> you can use two simultaneous Wi-Fi connections to decrease wireless "
#~ "traffic congestion and increase throughput."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Avec <abbr title=\"Dual Channel Wi-Fi AP Daemon\">Dual Channel WiFi</"
#~ "abbr>, vous pouvez utiliser deux connexions Wi-Fi simultanées pour "
#~ "réduire la congestion de la connexion sans fil et en augmenter le débit."
